          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1647964697848-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>soft cheese </strong>and 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100 ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan with the sun-dried tomatoes, give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce is starting to thicken</p><p>While the sauce is thickening, drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1647964714639-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1647964714639-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1647964714639-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1647964714639-x1000.jpg",
